    <item>
      <title>Aquilo Landing Preparation - What to Bring and How to Survive in Factorio Space Age</title>
      <link>https://factorioguides.com/space-age/aquilo/aquilo-guide/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://factorioguides.com/space-age/aquilo/aquilo-guide/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;pro-tip&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Aquilo survival at a glance:&lt;/strong&gt; Bring heating towers, rocket fuel, ice platforms, rocket turrets, and energy weapons. Land only after you have unlocked all previous planet sciences. Build a heat pipe grid first, then power, then defense, then science. Aquilo has no local resources except frozen ammonia -- everything else must be imported from other planets. Check https://factorioguides.com/space-age/guide/planet-order-guide/ for when to visit, and https://factorioguides.com/space-age/platform/space-platform-guide/ for the ship design that can reach the ice planet.&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;## Quick Reference 鈥?Aquilo&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Best Planet Order in Space Age - Which Planet to Visit First and Why</title>
      <link>https://factorioguides.com/space-age/guide/planet-order-guide/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://factorioguides.com/space-age/guide/planet-order-guide/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;pro-tip&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TL;DR: Vulcanus -&amp;gt; Fulgora -&amp;gt; Gleba -&amp;gt; Nauvis (scale up) -&amp;gt; Aquilo.&lt;/strong&gt; Visit Vulcanus first for the foundry — it doubles your iron and steel production instantly. See https://factorioguides.com/space-age/guide/vulcanus-guide/ for the full landing prep. Fulgora second for the electromagnetic plant and quality module loop. Gleba third for bioflux and agricultural science. Save Aquilo for last when your other planets are producing consistently.&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;section-head&#34;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Why Order Matters&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Factorio Space Age has four inner planets you must visit (Vulcanus, Fulgora, Gleba) plus the final planet (Aquilo). Each planet unlocks a permanent factory upgrade that changes how you produce things on all planets. The order you visit determines how quickly your base scales up.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vulcanus First Landing Guide - What to Do First in Factorio Space Age</title>
      <link>https://factorioguides.com/space-age/guide/vulcanus-guide/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://factorioguides.com/space-age/guide/vulcanus-guide/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;pro-tip&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vulcanus priority order:&lt;/strong&gt; Land -&amp;gt; Build a temporary base with solar panels and gun turrets -&amp;gt; Find lava -&amp;gt; Build foundry -&amp;gt; Unlock big drill -&amp;gt; Kill a small demolisher -&amp;gt; Build cliff explosives. Your entire Vulcanus strategy should revolve around unlocking the foundry as fast as possible. See https://factorioguides.com/space-age/vulcanus/lava-processing/ for the full molten metal production guide. Everything else is secondary.&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;## Quick Reference — Vulcanus&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Priority&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Task&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Key Building&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Key Item&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;1&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Land and build solar&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/icon/solar-panel.png&#34; alt=&#34;solar-panel&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Solar panel&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA; Solar panel&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/icon/steel-plate.png&#34; alt=&#34;steel-plate&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Steel plate&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA; Steel&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;2&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Mine tungsten&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/icon/big-mining-drill.png&#34; alt=&#34;big-mining-drill&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Big mining&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA; Big drill&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Tungsten carbide&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;3&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Build foundry&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/icon/foundry.png&#34; alt=&#34;foundry&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Foundry&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA; Foundry&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/icon/calcite.png&#34; alt=&#34;calcite&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Calcite&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA; Calcite&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;4&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Lava pumping&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/icon/offshore-pump.png&#34; alt=&#34;offshore-pump&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Offshore&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA; Pump&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Molten iron/copper&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Resource&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Recipe&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Input&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Output&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;Foundry Bonus&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Molten iron&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Smelting&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Lava + Calcite&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;500 fluid&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;+50% prod&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Molten copper&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Smelting&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Lava + Calcite&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;500 fluid&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;+50% prod&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Iron gears&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Casting&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;100 molten iron&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;20 gears&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;Direct craft&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Copper wire&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Casting&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;100 molten copper&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;40 wire&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;Direct craft&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;section-head&#34;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;What to Pack Before You Go&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Vulcanus has no trees, no water (except lava and sulfuric acid), and aggressive demolishers roaming the plains. Pack everything you need for the first 2-3 hours:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
